re: ProMED-mail Israeli spotted fever - Israel 20170907.5301015
---------------------------------------------------------------
Although Mediterranean spotted fever was commonly reported in Israel for several decades, rates have declined considerably in recent years. In fact, the disease is currently less common than its American counterpart [1]. The following chart was generated using the Gideon multi-graph tool [1] :
https://www.gideononline.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/RickettsiaIsrUS-2.png

